cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.GT (Game Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with simple games and their properties, such as the core and winning coalitions. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the computability of games and their complexity. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses logical reasoning to prove results about the properties of computable games. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the rationality of players in dealing with a limited number of alternatives. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also possible as the paper deals with the complexity of computing simple games.
